Initially they told us it would only be a
one hour wait but by the time one hour had

00:01:02.010 --> 00:01:07.049
passed we had waited so long that we figured
it was probably worth it to stay and now Sam

00:01:07.049 --> 00:01:08.110
is not very pleased.

