He's looking at me with evil eyes.

00:01:09.110 --> 00:01:10.110
Are you freaking kidding me.

00:01:10.110 --> 00:01:11.110
Sam is hiding behind the camera because he's
so angry that he had to wait for two hours.

00:01:11.110 --> 00:01:12.110
That now I'm being punished by having to be
on camera all alone.

00:01:12.110 --> 00:01:13.110
Okay, so if your'e looking to go afternoon
tea in Hong Kong.

00:01:13.110 --> 00:01:19.650
The Peninsula is the place to come.

00:01:19.650 --> 00:01:34.250
This is the oldest hotel in all of Hong Kong
and it's super popular.

00:01:34.250 --> 00:01:40.510
The lineups really speak for themselves.

00:01:40.510 --> 00:01:43.630
background music playing.

00:01:43.630 --> 00:01:45.719
Symphony orchestra.

00:01:45.719 --> 00:01:56.060
Mmmm, so I got my self a nice little tea cup
of mango tea.

00:01:56.060 --> 00:02:00.450
And it smells like fresh mangoes.

00:02:00.450 --> 00:02:01.920
So good.

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:03.380
Mmmm, tropical.

00:02:03.380 --> 00:02:05.580
Background music playing.

00:02:05.580 --> 00:02:09.970
We've already dug into the food.

00:02:09.970 --> 00:02:12.900
We couldn't help it.

00:02:12.900 --> 00:02:20.350
If you go to the bottom here we have the scones
which we can eat with the clotted cream and

00:02:20.350 --> 00:02:21.360
jam.

00:02:21.360 --> 00:02:27.910
Over here we have some nice finger sandwiches
with salmon, cucumber and up top we have the

00:02:27.910 --> 00:02:32.150
cakes and the macaroons and lots of other
treats.

00:02:32.150 --> 00:02:34.800
So here I'm preparing my scones with clotted
cream and jam.

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:38.890
This is a favorite of mine.

00:02:38.890 --> 00:02:39.890
Whenever I go to London to visit my friend
Rebecca I always end up staying at her house

00:02:39.890 --> 00:02:47.519
and I eat scones with clotted cream and jam
three times a day.

00:02:47.519 --> 00:02:48.519
I eat it for breakfast, for lunch and also
for my late night snack.

00:02:48.519 --> 00:02:52.970
So I always get fat when I go over there.

00:02:52.970 --> 00:02:54.810
Symphony music playing.

00:02:54.810 --> 00:02:56.650
