00:02:56.650 --> 00:02:59.110
The food was amazing.

00:02:59.110 --> 00:03:05.239
I think it was definitely worth the two hour
wait.

00:03:05.239 --> 00:03:11.989
Although, I would have preferred not having
to wait that long.

00:03:11.989 --> 00:03:19.080
Some favorites were the little lemon meringue
tarts in a chocolate shell.

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:25.900
Plus I really liked the scones with the clotted
cream.

00:03:25.900 --> 00:03:32.040
Then they had sandwiches with salmon that
were amazing.

00:03:32.040 --> 00:03:35.450
So I'm a happy girl.

00:03:35.450 --> 00:03:41.060
So I think it's kind of funny that we had
to wait two hours in line but it only took

00:03:41.060 --> 00:03:42.310
